      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"1. SUNSET SKYLIGHT is better than last start when fourth (16.35) from Box 6 at this track over 275m. Yet to miss the placings in five runs from this box, including two wins. Looks the one to beat on her best form. 2. GOLDEN HANDCUFFS turned in a moderate performance last time when seventh at this track over 275m behind South Crenshaw (16.62) in a Grade 6. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and two minor placings to his credit. One of the main contenders. 8. COOTAMUNDRA LAD turned in a solid run last start over 300m at Mandurah finishing 4th and beaten only 2.5 lengths (17.78). Solid record here at the distance winning four races. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings three times from four starts. Has ability and can measure up. 3. SUNSET AMANDA gets a chance to redeem an unplaced effort here last start.\",\"runners\":[1,2,8,3],\"exclusive\":false}",
